responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "D3C97A1043D51FBBF9638A9AA18EE012", "Paugh! That foul token is of goblin make. This is the design of the magics they have been given by the Sighted. It bears a curse, one of bloodlust against my tribe. Give it to me, I will crush it away, and purify the lingering essence within for my own uses. In the time between then and now, I propose an exchange of boons. ")
name: SQ_RVR_0036_Hrok_28
